Money Stuff =0A Here=E2=80=99s an insider trading hypothetical for you. I h=
ave a golf buddy who is a =0Asenior executive at a public company. One day =
on the course, sh =0A=0A=0A <> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomberg.com/click=3Fs=
=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12596346&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525=
&p=3D02122025>=0A=0A=0A=0AInsider betting=0A=0AHere=E2=80=99s an insider tr=
ading hypothetical for you. I have a golf buddy who is a =0Asenior executiv=
e at a public company. One day on the course, she tells me: =E2=80=9CMy =0A=
firm is going to announce a takeover of Anacott Steel at $15 per share; you=
 =0Ashould buy some.=E2=80=9D I go back to my office, open up my brokerage =
app, and am =0Aabout to buy 10,000 short-dated out-of-the-money call option=
s when I think: =0A=E2=80=9CWait, no, this is insider trading, I will get i=
n trouble for this.=E2=80=9D I close =0Athe app.=0A=0AInstead, I pick up my=
